[Course_Description]
Do you need higher engagement or leads for your personal or company page? Video is the secret weapon for driving business results in the digital era. This course offers five actionable strategies to increase brand awareness and engagement using video-based content. Discover how to improve your body language and get more comfortable in front of the camera, create the right calls to action, leverage unique hashtags, and more. Each strategy is accompanied by real-world examples showing the power of video in action. Plus, find out how to connect with award-winning instructor Nina Blankenship—digital marketing manager at LinkedIn—for more great tips.